"use strict";(self.webpackChunksozler_kitabi=self.webpackChunksozler_kitabi||[]).push([[3225],{3225:e=>{e.exports=JSON.parse("[{\"pageId\":1,\"rawText\":\"Alt\u0131nc\u0131 S\xf6z\\n\\n\u0628\u0650\u0633\u0652\u0645\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0645\u0670\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u064e\u062d\u0656\u064a\u0645\u0650\\n\\n\u0627\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u064e \u0627\u0634\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0631\u0670\u0649 \u0645\u0650\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0624\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0646\u0656\u064a\u0646\u064e \u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0641\u064f\u0633\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0628\u0650\u0627\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0645\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062c\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0629\u064e\\n\\nNefis ve mal\u0131n\u0131 Cenab-\u0131 Hakk\u2019a satmak ve ona abd olmak ve asker olmak; ne kadar k\xe2rl\u0131 bir ticaret, ne kadar \u015ferefli bir r\xfctbe oldu\u011funu anlamak istersen \u015fu temsil\xee hik\xe2yeci\u011fi dinle:\\n\\nBir zaman bir padi\u015fah, raiyetinden iki adama, her birisine emaneten birer \xe7iftlik verir ki i\xe7inde fabrika, makine, at, silah gibi her \u015fey var. Fakat f\u0131rt\u0131nal\u0131 bir muharebe zaman\u0131 oldu\u011fundan hi\xe7bir \u015fey karar\u0131nda kalmaz. Ya mahvolur veya tebedd\xfcl eder gider. Padi\u015fah, o iki nefere kemal-i merhametinden bir yaver-i ekremini g\xf6nderdi. Gayet merhametk\xe2r bir ferman ile onlara diyordu:\\n\\n\u201cElinizde olan emanetimi bana sat\u0131n\u0131z. T\xe2 sizin i\xe7in muhafaza edeyim, beyhude zayi olmas\u0131n. Hem muharebe bittikten sonra size daha g\xfczel bir surette iade edece\u011fim. Hem g\xfcya o emanet mal\u0131n\u0131zd\u0131r, pek b\xfcy\xfck bir fiyat size verece\u011fim. Hem o makine ve fabrikadaki \xe2letler, benim nam\u0131mla ve benim tezg\xe2h\u0131mda i\u015flettirilecek. Hem fiyat\u0131 hem \xfccretleri, birden bine y\xfckselecek. B\xfct\xfcn o k\xe2r\u0131 size verece\u011fim. Hem de siz, \xe2ciz ve fakirsiniz. O koca i\u015flerin masarifat\u0131n\u0131 tedarik edemezsiniz. B\xfct\xfcn masarifat\u0131 ve levaz\u0131mat\u0131, ben deruhte ederim. B\xfct\xfcn v\xe2ridat\u0131 ve menfaati size verece\u011fim. Hem de terhisat zaman\u0131na kadar elinizde b\u0131rakaca\u011f\u0131m. \u0130\u015fte be\u015f mertebe k\xe2r i\xe7inde k\xe2r\u2026\\n\\nE\u011fer bana satmazsan\u0131z zaten g\xf6r\xfcyorsunuz ki hi\xe7 kimse elindekini muhafaza edemiyor. Herkes gibi elinizden \xe7\u0131kacakt\u0131r. Hem beyhude gidecek. Hem o y\xfcksek fiyattan mahrum kalacaks\u0131n\u0131z. Hem o nazik, k\u0131ymettar \xe2letler, mizanlar, istimal edilecek \u015fahane madenler ve i\u015fler bulmad\u0131\u011f\u0131ndan b\xfct\xfcn b\xfct\xfcn k\u0131ymetten d\xfc\u015fecekler. Hem idare ve muhafaza zahmeti ve k\xfclfeti ba\u015f\u0131n\u0131za kalacak. Hem emanette h\u0131yanet cezas\u0131n\u0131 g\xf6receksiniz. \u0130\u015fte be\u015f derece hasaret i\xe7inde hasaret\u2026\\n\\nHem de bana satmak ise bana asker olup benim nam\u0131mla tasarruf etmek demektir. \xc2di bir esir ve ba\u015f\u0131 bozu\u011fa bedel, \xe2l\xee bir padi\u015fah\u0131n has, serbest bir yaver-i askeri olursunuz.\u201d\\n\\nOnlar, \u015fu iltifat\u0131 ve ferman\u0131 dinledikten sonra o iki adamdan akl\u0131 ba\u015f\u0131nda olan\u0131 dedi:\\n\\n\u2014 Ba\u015f \xfcst\xfcne, ben maaliftihar satar\u0131m. Hem bin te\u015fekk\xfcr ederim.\\n\\nDi\u011feri ma\u011frur, nefsi firavunla\u015fm\u0131\u015f, hodbin, ayya\u015f, g\xfcya ebed\xee o \xe7iftlikte kalacak gibi d\xfcnya zelzelelerinden, da\u011fda\u011falar\u0131ndan haberi yok. Dedi:\\n\\n\u2014 Yok! Padi\u015fah kimdir? Ben m\xfclk\xfcm\xfc satmam, keyfimi bozmam\u2026\\n\\nBiraz zaman sonra birinci adam \xf6yle bir mertebeye \xe7\u0131kt\u0131 ki herkes haline g\u0131pta ederdi. Padi\u015fah\u0131n l\xfctfuna mazhar olmu\u015f, has saray\u0131nda saadetle ya\u015f\u0131yor. Di\u011feri, \xf6yle bir hale giriftar olmu\u015f ki hem herkes ona ac\u0131yor hem de \u201cM\xfcstahak!\u201d diyor. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc hatas\u0131n\u0131n neticesi olarak hem saadeti ve m\xfclk\xfc gitmi\u015f hem ceza ve azap \xe7ekiyor.\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte ey nefs-i p\xfcr-heves! \u015eu misalin d\xfcrb\xfcn\xfc ile hakikatin y\xfcz\xfcne bak. Amma o padi\u015fah ise ezel ebed Sultan\u0131 olan Rabb\u2019in, H\xe2l\u0131k\u2019\u0131nd\u0131r. Ve o \xe7iftlikler, makineler, \xe2letler, mizanlar ise senin daire-i hayat\u0131n i\xe7indeki m\xe2melekin ve o m\xe2melekin i\xe7indeki cisim, ruh ve kalbin ve onlar i\xe7indeki g\xf6z ve dil, ak\u0131l ve hayal gibi zahir\xee ve b\xe2t\u0131n\xee h\xe2sselerindir. Ve o yaver-i ekrem ise Resul-i Ker\xeem\u2019dir. Ve o ferman-\u0131 ahkem ise Kur\u2019an-\u0131 Hak\xeem\u2019dir ki bahsinde bulundu\u011fumuz ticaret-i az\xeemeyi, \u015fu \xe2yetle ilan ediyor:\\n\\n\u0627\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u064e \u0627\u0634\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0631\u0670\u0649 \u0645\u0650\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0624\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0646\u0656\u064a\u0646\u064e \u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0641\u064f\u0633\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0628\u0650\u0627\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0645\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062c\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0629\u064e\\n\\nVe o dalgal\u0131 muharebe meydan\u0131 ise \u015fu f\u0131rt\u0131nal\u0131 d\xfcnya y\xfcz\xfcd\xfcr ki durmuyor, d\xf6n\xfcyor, bozuluyor ve her insan\u0131n akl\u0131na \u015fu fikri veriyor: \u201cMadem her \u015fey elimizden \xe7\u0131kacak, f\xe2ni olup kaybolacak. Acaba b\xe2kiye tebdil edip ibka etmek \xe7aresi yok mu?\u201d deyip d\xfc\u015f\xfcn\xfcrken birden semav\xee sad\xe2-y\u0131 Kur\u2019an i\u015fitiliyor. Der: \u201cEvet, var. Hem be\u015f mertebe k\xe2rl\u0131 bir surette g\xfczel ve rahat bir \xe7aresi var.\u201d\\n\\nSual: Nedir?\\n\\nElcevap: Emaneti, sahib-i hakikisine satmak.\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte o sat\u0131\u015fta, be\u015f derece k\xe2r i\xe7inde k\xe2r var.\",\"modernText\":\"Alt\u0131nc\u0131 S\xf6z\\n\\n[[Bismillahirrahmanirrah\xeem|\u0628\u0650\u0633\u0652\u0645\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0645\u0670\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u064e\u062d\u0656\u064a\u0645\u0650|Rahman ve Rahim olan Allah'\u0131n ad\u0131yla]]\\n\\n[[Allah, m\xfcminlerden canlar\u0131n\u0131 ve mallar\u0131n\u0131, kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131nda onlara cenneti vermek \xfczere sat\u0131n alm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r (Tevbe Suresi, 111. Ayet)|\u0627\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u064e \u0627\u0634\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0631\u0670\u0649 \u0645\u0650\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0624\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0646\u0656\u064a\u0646\u064e \u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0641\u064f\u0633\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0628\u0650\u0627\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0645\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062c\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0629\u064e|]]\\n\\nNefis ve mal\u0131n\u0131 [[Allah'a|Cenab-\u0131 Hakk\u2019a|Hakk olan y\xfcce Allah'a]] satmak ve ona [[kul olmak|abd olmak|]] ve asker olmak; ne kadar k\xe2rl\u0131 bir ticaret, ne kadar \u015ferefli bir r\xfctbe oldu\u011funu anlamak istersen \u015fu [[benzetmeli|temsil\xee|ger\xe7e\u011fi hikaye yoluyla anlatan]] hik\xe2yeci\u011fi dinle:\\n\\nBir zaman bir padi\u015fah, [[halk\u0131ndan|raiyetinden|idaresi alt\u0131ndakilerden]] iki adama, her birisine [[emanet olarak|emaneten|geri al\u0131nmak \xfczere ge\xe7ici olarak]] birer \xe7iftlik verir ki i\xe7inde fabrika, makine, at, silah gibi her \u015fey var. Fakat f\u0131rt\u0131nal\u0131 bir [[sava\u015f|muharebe|\xe7arp\u0131\u015fma]] zaman\u0131 oldu\u011fundan hi\xe7bir \u015fey [[yerinde|karar\u0131nda|sabit, de\u011fi\u015fmeden]] kalmaz. Ya mahvolur veya [[de\u011fi\u015fir|tebedd\xfcl eder|ba\u015fkala\u015f\u0131r]] gider. Padi\u015fah, o iki [[askere|nefere|ere]] [[sonsuz merhametinden|kemal-i merhametinden|merhametinin m\xfckemmelli\u011finden]] bir [[en \u015ferefli yaverini|yaver-i ekremini|padi\u015fah\u0131n en yak\u0131n ve en \u015ferefli yard\u0131mc\u0131s\u0131n\u0131]] g\xf6nderdi. Gayet merhametk\xe2r bir [[emir|ferman|padi\u015fah emri]] ile onlara diyordu:\\n\\n\u201cElinizde olan emanetimi bana sat\u0131n\u0131z. T\xe2 sizin i\xe7in [[koruyay\u0131m|muhafaza edeyim|]], [[bo\u015funa|beyhude|faydas\u0131z yere]] [[kaybolmas\u0131n|zayi olmas\u0131n|ziyan olmas\u0131n]]. Hem [[sava\u015f|muharebe|]] bittikten sonra size daha g\xfczel bir [[\u015fekilde|surette|bi\xe7imde]] [[geri verece\u011fim|iade edece\u011fim|]]. Hem g\xfcya o emanet mal\u0131n\u0131zd\u0131r, pek b\xfcy\xfck bir fiyat size verece\u011fim. Hem o makine ve fabrikadaki \xe2letler, benim [[ad\u0131mla|nam\u0131mla|benim ismimle]] ve benim tezg\xe2h\u0131mda i\u015flettirilecek. Hem fiyat\u0131 hem \xfccretleri, birden bine y\xfckselecek. B\xfct\xfcn o k\xe2r\u0131 size verece\u011fim. Hem de siz, [[g\xfc\xe7s\xfcz|\xe2ciz|elden bir \u015fey gelmeyen]] ve fakirsiniz. O koca i\u015flerin [[masraflar\u0131n\u0131|masarifat\u0131n\u0131|giderlerini]] [[kar\u015f\u0131layamazs\u0131n\u0131z|tedarik edemezsiniz|bulup temin edemezsiniz]]. B\xfct\xfcn [[masraflar\u0131|masarifat\u0131|]] ve [[gere\xe7leri|levaz\u0131mat\u0131|gerekli malzemeleri]], ben [[\xfcstlenirim|deruhte ederim|\xfczerime al\u0131r\u0131m]]. B\xfct\xfcn [[gelirleri|v\xe2ridat\u0131|kazan\xe7lar\u0131]] ve [[faydas\u0131|menfaati|kar\u0131]] size verece\u011fim. Hem de [[askerli\u011fin biti\u015f zaman\u0131na|terhisat zaman\u0131na|g\xf6revden ayr\u0131lma vaktine]] kadar elinizde b\u0131rakaca\u011f\u0131m. \u0130\u015fte be\u015f [[derece|mertebe|kat]] k\xe2r i\xe7inde k\xe2r\u2026\\n\\nE\u011fer bana satmazsan\u0131z zaten g\xf6r\xfcyorsunuz ki hi\xe7 kimse elindekini [[koruyam\u0131yor|muhafaza edemiyor|]]. Herkes gibi elinizden \xe7\u0131kacakt\u0131r. Hem [[bo\u015funa|beyhude|]] gidecek. Hem o y\xfcksek fiyattan mahrum kalacaks\u0131n\u0131z. Hem o nazik, [[de\u011ferli|k\u0131ymettar|k\u0131ymetli]] \xe2letler, [[\xf6l\xe7\xfcler|mizanlar|tart\u0131lar, dengeler]], [[kullan\u0131lacak|istimal edilecek|]] \u015fahane madenler ve i\u015fler bulmad\u0131\u011f\u0131ndan b\xfct\xfcn b\xfct\xfcn k\u0131ymetten d\xfc\u015fecekler. Hem idare ve muhafaza zahmeti ve [[zorlu\u011fu|k\xfclfeti|y\xfck\xfc, s\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131s\u0131]] ba\u015f\u0131n\u0131za kalacak. Hem emanette [[hainlik|h\u0131yanet|emanete sadakatsizlik]] cezas\u0131n\u0131 g\xf6receksiniz. \u0130\u015fte be\u015f derece [[zarar|hasaret|ziyan]] i\xe7inde [[zarar|hasaret|ziyan]]\u2026\\n\\nHem de bana satmak ise bana asker olup benim [[ad\u0131mla|nam\u0131mla|]] [[kullanmak|tasarruf etmek|diledi\u011fi gibi y\xf6netmek]] demektir. [[s\u0131radan|\xc2di|basit]] bir esir ve [[d\xfczensiz askere|ba\u015f\u0131 bozu\u011fa|sivil halktan olan ve askeri d\xfczeni olmayan kimseye]] [[kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131k|bedel|yerine]], [[y\xfcce|\xe2l\xee|y\xfcksek]] bir padi\u015fah\u0131n [[\xf6zel|has|se\xe7kin]], serbest bir [[askeri yard\u0131mc\u0131|yaver-i askeri|padi\u015faha yak\u0131n asker]] olursunuz.\u201d\\n\\nOnlar, \u015fu [[g\xfczel s\xf6z\xfc|iltifat\u0131|g\xf6n\xfcl al\u0131c\u0131 davran\u0131\u015f\u0131]] ve [[emri|ferman\u0131|]] dinledikten sonra o iki adamdan akl\u0131 ba\u015f\u0131nda olan\u0131 dedi:\\n\\n\u2014 Ba\u015f \xfcst\xfcne, ben [[iftiharla|maaliftihar|\xf6v\xfcnerek, gurur duyarak]] satar\u0131m. Hem bin te\u015fekk\xfcr ederim.\\n\\nDi\u011feri [[gururlu|ma\u011frur|kibirli]], nefsi firavunla\u015fm\u0131\u015f, [[bencil|hodbin|kendini be\u011fenen]], ayya\u015f, g\xfcya [[sonsuz|ebed\xee|\xf6l\xfcms\xfcz]] o \xe7iftlikte kalacak gibi d\xfcnya zelzelelerinden, [[g\xfcr\xfclt\xfclerinden|da\u011fda\u011falar\u0131ndan|s\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131lar\u0131ndan, tela\u015flar\u0131ndan]] haberi yok. Dedi:\\n\\n\u2014 Yok! Padi\u015fah kimdir? Ben m\xfclk\xfcm\xfc satmam, keyfimi bozmam\u2026\\n\\nBiraz zaman sonra birinci adam \xf6yle bir [[dereceye|mertebeye|makama]] \xe7\u0131kt\u0131 ki herkes haline g\u0131pta ederdi. Padi\u015fah\u0131n [[iyili\u011fine|l\xfctfuna|ihsan\u0131na]] [[eri\u015fmi\u015f|mazhar olmu\u015f|nail olmu\u015f]], [[\xf6zel|has|]] saray\u0131nda [[mutlulukla|saadetle|]] ya\u015f\u0131yor. Di\u011feri, \xf6yle bir hale [[tutulmu\u015f|giriftar olmu\u015f|yakalanm\u0131\u015f]] ki hem herkes ona ac\u0131yor hem de \u201c[[hak etmi\u015f|M\xfcstahak|lay\u0131k]]!\u201d diyor. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc hatas\u0131n\u0131n neticesi olarak hem [[mutlulu\u011fu|saadeti|]] ve m\xfclk\xfc gitmi\u015f hem ceza ve azap \xe7ekiyor.\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte ey [[heves dolu nefis|nefs-i p\xfcr-heves|arzular\u0131na \xe7ok d\xfc\u015fk\xfcn nefis]]! \u015eu [[\xf6rne\u011fin|misalin|benzetmenin]] d\xfcrb\xfcn\xfc ile [[ger\xe7e\u011fin|hakikatin|]] y\xfcz\xfcne bak. Amma o padi\u015fah ise [[ba\u015flang\u0131c\u0131 olmayan ge\xe7mi\u015f|ezel|]] [[sonu olmayan gelecek|ebed|]] Sultan\u0131 olan Rabb\u2019in, [[Yarat\u0131c\u0131nd\u0131r|H\xe2l\u0131k\u2019\u0131nd\u0131r|]]. Ve o \xe7iftlikler, makineler, \xe2letler, [[\xf6l\xe7\xfcler|mizanlar|tart\u0131lar]] ise senin [[hayat dairen|daire-i hayat\u0131n|ya\u015fam alan\u0131n]] i\xe7indeki [[varl\u0131\u011f\u0131n|m\xe2melekin|sahip oldu\u011fun her \u015fey]] ve o [[varl\u0131\u011f\u0131n|m\xe2melekin|]] i\xe7indeki [[beden|cisim|v\xfccut]], ruh ve kalbin ve onlar i\xe7indeki g\xf6z ve dil, ak\u0131l ve hayal gibi [[g\xf6r\xfcnen|zahir\xee|d\u0131\u015fa ait]] ve [[g\xf6r\xfcnmeyen|b\xe2t\u0131n\xee|i\xe7e ait, manevi]] [[duyular\u0131nd\u0131r|h\xe2sselerindir|hissiyatlar\u0131nd\u0131r]]. Ve o [[en \u015ferefli yaver|yaver-i ekrem|peygamber]] ise [[C\xf6mert ve \u015ferefli El\xe7i|Resul-i Ker\xeem\u2019dir|Hz. Muhammed (a.s.m)]]. Ve o [[en sa\u011flam ferman|ferman-\u0131 ahkem|h\xfckm\xfc en ge\xe7erli emir]] ise [[Hikmetli Kur'an|Kur\u2019an-\u0131 Hak\xeem\u2019dir|her s\xf6z\xfcnde hikmet bulunan Kur'an]] ki [[konusunda|bahsinde|s\xf6z\xfcnde]] bulundu\u011fumuz [[b\xfcy\xfck ticareti|ticaret-i az\xeemeyi|muazzam al\u0131\u015fveri\u015fi]], \u015fu \xe2yetle ilan ediyor:\\n\\n:: [[Allah, m\xfcminlerden canlar\u0131n\u0131 ve mallar\u0131n\u0131, kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131nda onlara cenneti vermek \xfczere sat\u0131n alm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r|\u0627\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u064e \u0627\u0634\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0631\u0670\u0649 \u0645\u0650\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0624\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0646\u0656\u064a\u0646\u064e \u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0641\u064f\u0633\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0628\u0650\u0627\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0645\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062c\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0629\u064e|]]\\n\\nVe o dalgal\u0131 [[sava\u015f|muharebe|]] meydan\u0131 ise \u015fu f\u0131rt\u0131nal\u0131 d\xfcnya y\xfcz\xfcd\xfcr ki durmuyor, d\xf6n\xfcyor, bozuluyor ve her insan\u0131n akl\u0131na \u015fu fikri veriyor: \u201cMadem her \u015fey elimizden \xe7\u0131kacak, [[ge\xe7ici|f\xe2ni|\xf6l\xfcml\xfc]] olup kaybolacak. Acaba [[kal\u0131c\u0131 olana|b\xe2kiye|ebedi olana]] [[d\xf6n\xfc\u015ft\xfcr\xfcp|tebdil edip|de\u011fi\u015ftirip]] [[ebedile\u015ftirmek|ibka etmek|kal\u0131c\u0131 k\u0131lmak]] \xe7aresi yok mu?\u201d deyip d\xfc\u015f\xfcn\xfcrken birden [[g\xf6kten gelen|semav\xee|ilahi]] [[Kur'an'\u0131n sesi|sad\xe2-y\u0131 Kur\u2019an|]] i\u015fitiliyor. Der: \u201cEvet, var. Hem be\u015f [[derece|mertebe|]] k\xe2rl\u0131 bir [[\u015fekilde|surette|]] g\xfczel ve rahat bir \xe7aresi var.\u201d\\n\\n[[Soru|Sual|]]: Nedir?\\n\\n[[Cevap|Elcevap|]]: Emaneti, [[ger\xe7ek sahibine|sahib-i hakikisine|]] satmak.\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte o sat\u0131\u015fta, be\u015f derece k\xe2r i\xe7inde k\xe2r var.\",\"processedBy\":\"\ud83e\udde0 Gemini 3.0 Pro (Web - Manuel) on 2025.12.17-18:17\",\"lastUpdated\":\"2025.12.25-21:49\",\"oldText\":\"Alt\u0131nc\u0131 S\xf6z\\n\\n[[\u0628\u0650\u0633\u0652\u0645\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0645\u0670\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u0651\u064e\u062d\u0656\u064a\u0645\u0650|Bismillahirrahmanirrah\xeem|Rahman ve Rahim olan Allah'\u0131n ad\u0131yla]]\\n\\n[[\u0627\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u064e \u0627\u0634\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0631\u0670\u0649 \u0645\u0650\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0624\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0646\u0656\u064a\u0646\u064e \u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0641\u064f\u0633\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0628\u0650\u0627\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0645\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062c\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0629\u064e|Allah, m\xfcminlerden canlar\u0131n\u0131 ve mallar\u0131n\u0131, kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131nda onlara cenneti vermek \xfczere sat\u0131n alm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r (Tevbe Suresi, 111. Ayet)]]\\n\\nNefis ve mal\u0131n\u0131 [[Cenab-\u0131 Hakk\u2019a|Allah'a|Hakk olan y\xfcce Allah'a]] satmak ve ona [[abd olmak|kul olmak]] ve asker olmak; ne kadar k\xe2rl\u0131 bir ticaret, ne kadar \u015ferefli bir r\xfctbe oldu\u011funu anlamak istersen \u015fu [[temsil\xee|benzetmeli|ger\xe7e\u011fi hikaye yoluyla anlatan]] hik\xe2yeci\u011fi dinle:\\n\\nBir zaman bir padi\u015fah, [[raiyetinden|halk\u0131ndan|idaresi alt\u0131ndakilerden]] iki adama, her birisine [[emaneten|emanet olarak|geri al\u0131nmak \xfczere ge\xe7ici olarak]] birer \xe7iftlik verir ki i\xe7inde fabrika, makine, at, silah gibi her \u015fey var. Fakat f\u0131rt\u0131nal\u0131 bir [[muharebe|sava\u015f|\xe7arp\u0131\u015fma]] zaman\u0131 oldu\u011fundan hi\xe7bir \u015fey [[karar\u0131nda|yerinde|sabit, de\u011fi\u015fmeden]] kalmaz. Ya mahvolur veya [[tebedd\xfcl eder|de\u011fi\u015fir|ba\u015fkala\u015f\u0131r]] gider. Padi\u015fah, o iki [[nefere|askere|ere]] [[kemal-i merhametinden|sonsuz merhametinden|merhametinin m\xfckemmelli\u011finden]] bir [[yaver-i ekremini|en \u015ferefli yaverini|padi\u015fah\u0131n en yak\u0131n ve en \u015ferefli yard\u0131mc\u0131s\u0131n\u0131]] g\xf6nderdi. Gayet merhametk\xe2r bir [[ferman|emir|padi\u015fah emri]] ile onlara diyordu:\\n\\n\u201cElinizde olan emanetimi bana sat\u0131n\u0131z. T\xe2 sizin i\xe7in [[muhafaza edeyim|koruyay\u0131m]], [[beyhude|bo\u015funa|faydas\u0131z yere]] [[zayi olmas\u0131n|kaybolmas\u0131n|ziyan olmas\u0131n]]. Hem [[muharebe|sava\u015f]] bittikten sonra size daha g\xfczel bir [[surette|\u015fekilde|bi\xe7imde]] [[iade edece\u011fim|geri verece\u011fim]]. Hem g\xfcya o emanet mal\u0131n\u0131zd\u0131r, pek b\xfcy\xfck bir fiyat size verece\u011fim. Hem o makine ve fabrikadaki \xe2letler, benim [[nam\u0131mla|ad\u0131mla|benim ismimle]] ve benim tezg\xe2h\u0131mda i\u015flettirilecek. Hem fiyat\u0131 hem \xfccretleri, birden bine y\xfckselecek. B\xfct\xfcn o k\xe2r\u0131 size verece\u011fim. Hem de siz, [[\xe2ciz|g\xfc\xe7s\xfcz|elden bir \u015fey gelmeyen]] ve fakirsiniz. O koca i\u015flerin [[masarifat\u0131n\u0131|masraflar\u0131n\u0131|giderlerini]] [[tedarik edemezsiniz|kar\u015f\u0131layamazs\u0131n\u0131z|bulup temin edemezsiniz]]. B\xfct\xfcn [[masarifat\u0131|masraflar\u0131]] ve [[levaz\u0131mat\u0131|gere\xe7leri|gerekli malzemeleri]], ben [[deruhte ederim|\xfcstlenirim|\xfczerime al\u0131r\u0131m]]. B\xfct\xfcn [[v\xe2ridat\u0131|gelirleri|kazan\xe7lar\u0131]] ve [[menfaati|faydas\u0131|kar\u0131]] size verece\u011fim. Hem de [[terhisat zaman\u0131na|askerli\u011fin biti\u015f zaman\u0131na|g\xf6revden ayr\u0131lma vaktine]] kadar elinizde b\u0131rakaca\u011f\u0131m. \u0130\u015fte be\u015f [[mertebe|derece|kat]] k\xe2r i\xe7inde k\xe2r\u2026\\n\\nE\u011fer bana satmazsan\u0131z zaten g\xf6r\xfcyorsunuz ki hi\xe7 kimse elindekini [[muhafaza edemiyor|koruyam\u0131yor]]. Herkes gibi elinizden \xe7\u0131kacakt\u0131r. Hem [[beyhude|bo\u015funa]] gidecek. Hem o y\xfcksek fiyattan mahrum kalacaks\u0131n\u0131z. Hem o nazik, [[k\u0131ymettar|de\u011ferli|k\u0131ymetli]] \xe2letler, [[mizanlar|\xf6l\xe7\xfcler|tart\u0131lar, dengeler]], [[istimal edilecek|kullan\u0131lacak]] \u015fahane madenler ve i\u015fler bulmad\u0131\u011f\u0131ndan b\xfct\xfcn b\xfct\xfcn k\u0131ymetten d\xfc\u015fecekler. Hem idare ve muhafaza zahmeti ve [[k\xfclfeti|zorlu\u011fu|y\xfck\xfc, s\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131s\u0131]] ba\u015f\u0131n\u0131za kalacak. Hem emanette [[h\u0131yanet|hainlik|emanete sadakatsizlik]] cezas\u0131n\u0131 g\xf6receksiniz. \u0130\u015fte be\u015f derece [[hasaret|zarar|ziyan]] i\xe7inde [[hasaret|zarar|ziyan]]\u2026\\n\\nHem de bana satmak ise bana asker olup benim [[nam\u0131mla|ad\u0131mla]] [[tasarruf etmek|kullanmak|diledi\u011fi gibi y\xf6netmek]] demektir. [[\xc2di|s\u0131radan|basit]] bir esir ve [[ba\u015f\u0131 bozu\u011fa|d\xfczensiz askere|sivil halktan olan ve askeri d\xfczeni olmayan kimseye]] [[bedel|kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131k|yerine]], [[\xe2l\xee|y\xfcce|y\xfcksek]] bir padi\u015fah\u0131n [[has|\xf6zel|se\xe7kin]], serbest bir [[yaver-i askeri|askeri yard\u0131mc\u0131|padi\u015faha yak\u0131n asker]] olursunuz.\u201d\\n\\nOnlar, \u015fu [[iltifat\u0131|g\xfczel s\xf6z\xfc|g\xf6n\xfcl al\u0131c\u0131 davran\u0131\u015f\u0131]] ve [[ferman\u0131|emri]] dinledikten sonra o iki adamdan akl\u0131 ba\u015f\u0131nda olan\u0131 dedi:\\n\\n\u2014 Ba\u015f \xfcst\xfcne, ben [[maaliftihar|iftiharla|\xf6v\xfcnerek, gurur duyarak]] satar\u0131m. Hem bin te\u015fekk\xfcr ederim.\\n\\nDi\u011feri [[ma\u011frur|gururlu|kibirli]], nefsi firavunla\u015fm\u0131\u015f, [[hodbin|bencil|kendini be\u011fenen]], ayya\u015f, g\xfcya [[ebed\xee|sonsuz|\xf6l\xfcms\xfcz]] o \xe7iftlikte kalacak gibi d\xfcnya zelzelelerinden, [[da\u011fda\u011falar\u0131ndan|g\xfcr\xfclt\xfclerinden|s\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131lar\u0131ndan, tela\u015flar\u0131ndan]] haberi yok. Dedi:\\n\\n\u2014 Yok! Padi\u015fah kimdir? Ben m\xfclk\xfcm\xfc satmam, keyfimi bozmam\u2026\\n\\nBiraz zaman sonra birinci adam \xf6yle bir [[mertebeye|dereceye|makama]] \xe7\u0131kt\u0131 ki herkes haline g\u0131pta ederdi. Padi\u015fah\u0131n [[l\xfctfuna|iyili\u011fine|ihsan\u0131na]] [[mazhar olmu\u015f|eri\u015fmi\u015f|nail olmu\u015f]], [[has|\xf6zel]] saray\u0131nda [[saadetle|mutlulukla]] ya\u015f\u0131yor. Di\u011feri, \xf6yle bir hale [[giriftar olmu\u015f|tutulmu\u015f|yakalanm\u0131\u015f]] ki hem herkes ona ac\u0131yor hem de \u201c[[M\xfcstahak|hak etmi\u015f|lay\u0131k]]!\u201d diyor. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc hatas\u0131n\u0131n neticesi olarak hem [[saadeti|mutlulu\u011fu]] ve m\xfclk\xfc gitmi\u015f hem ceza ve azap \xe7ekiyor.\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte ey [[nefs-i p\xfcr-heves|heves dolu nefis|arzular\u0131na \xe7ok d\xfc\u015fk\xfcn nefis]]! \u015eu [[misalin|\xf6rne\u011fin|benzetmenin]] d\xfcrb\xfcn\xfc ile [[hakikatin|ger\xe7e\u011fin]] y\xfcz\xfcne bak. Amma o padi\u015fah ise [[ezel|ba\u015flang\u0131c\u0131 olmayan ge\xe7mi\u015f]] [[ebed|sonu olmayan gelecek]] Sultan\u0131 olan Rabb\u2019in, [[H\xe2l\u0131k\u2019\u0131nd\u0131r|Yarat\u0131c\u0131nd\u0131r]]. Ve o \xe7iftlikler, makineler, \xe2letler, [[mizanlar|\xf6l\xe7\xfcler|tart\u0131lar]] ise senin [[daire-i hayat\u0131n|hayat dairen|ya\u015fam alan\u0131n]] i\xe7indeki [[m\xe2melekin|varl\u0131\u011f\u0131n|sahip oldu\u011fun her \u015fey]] ve o [[m\xe2melekin|varl\u0131\u011f\u0131n]] i\xe7indeki [[cisim|beden|v\xfccut]], ruh ve kalbin ve onlar i\xe7indeki g\xf6z ve dil, ak\u0131l ve hayal gibi [[zahir\xee|g\xf6r\xfcnen|d\u0131\u015fa ait]] ve [[b\xe2t\u0131n\xee|g\xf6r\xfcnmeyen|i\xe7e ait, manevi]] [[h\xe2sselerindir|duyular\u0131nd\u0131r|hissiyatlar\u0131nd\u0131r]]. Ve o [[yaver-i ekrem|en \u015ferefli yaver|peygamber]] ise [[Resul-i Ker\xeem\u2019dir|C\xf6mert ve \u015ferefli El\xe7i|Hz. Muhammed (a.s.m)]]. Ve o [[ferman-\u0131 ahkem|en sa\u011flam ferman|h\xfckm\xfc en ge\xe7erli emir]] ise [[Kur\u2019an-\u0131 Hak\xeem\u2019dir|Hikmetli Kur'an|her s\xf6z\xfcnde hikmet bulunan Kur'an]] ki [[bahsinde|konusunda|s\xf6z\xfcnde]] bulundu\u011fumuz [[ticaret-i az\xeemeyi|b\xfcy\xfck ticareti|muazzam al\u0131\u015fveri\u015fi]], \u015fu \xe2yetle ilan ediyor:\\n\\n:: [[\u0627\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u0670\u0647\u064e \u0627\u0634\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0631\u0670\u0649 \u0645\u0650\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0624\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0646\u0656\u064a\u0646\u064e \u0627\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0641\u064f\u0633\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0628\u0650\u0627\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0647\u064f\u0645\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062c\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0629\u064e|Allah, m\xfcminlerden canlar\u0131n\u0131 ve mallar\u0131n\u0131, kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131nda onlara cenneti vermek \xfczere sat\u0131n alm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r]]\\n\\nVe o dalgal\u0131 [[muharebe|sava\u015f]] meydan\u0131 ise \u015fu f\u0131rt\u0131nal\u0131 d\xfcnya y\xfcz\xfcd\xfcr ki durmuyor, d\xf6n\xfcyor, bozuluyor ve her insan\u0131n akl\u0131na \u015fu fikri veriyor: \u201cMadem her \u015fey elimizden \xe7\u0131kacak, [[f\xe2ni|ge\xe7ici|\xf6l\xfcml\xfc]] olup kaybolacak. Acaba [[b\xe2kiye|kal\u0131c\u0131 olana|ebedi olana]] [[tebdil edip|d\xf6n\xfc\u015ft\xfcr\xfcp|de\u011fi\u015ftirip]] [[ibka etmek|ebedile\u015ftirmek|kal\u0131c\u0131 k\u0131lmak]] \xe7aresi yok mu?\u201d deyip d\xfc\u015f\xfcn\xfcrken birden [[semav\xee|g\xf6kten gelen|ilahi]] [[sad\xe2-y\u0131 Kur\u2019an|Kur'an'\u0131n sesi]] i\u015fitiliyor. Der: \u201cEvet, var. Hem be\u015f [[mertebe|derece]] k\xe2rl\u0131 bir [[surette|\u015fekilde]] g\xfczel ve rahat bir \xe7aresi var.\u201d\\n\\n[[Sual|Soru]]: Nedir?\\n\\n[[Elcevap|Cevap]]: Emaneti, [[sahib-i hakikisine|ger\xe7ek sahibine]] satmak.\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte o sat\u0131\u015fta, be\u015f derece k\xe2r i\xe7inde k\xe2r var.\"},{\"pageId\":2,\"rawText\":\"Birinci k\xe2r: F\xe2ni mal, beka bulur. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc Kayyum-u B\xe2ki olan Zat-\u0131 Z\xfclcelal\u2019e verilen ve onun yolunda sarf edilen \u015fu \xf6mr-\xfc z\xe2il, b\xe2kiye ink\u0131lab eder, b\xe2ki meyveler verir. O vakit \xf6m\xfcr dakikalar\u0131, \xe2deta tohumlar, \xe7ekirdekler h\xfckm\xfcnde zahiren fena bulur, \xe7\xfcr\xfcr. Fakat \xe2lem-i bekada, saadet \xe7i\xe7ekleri a\xe7arlar ve s\xfcmb\xfcllenirler. Ve \xe2lem-i berzahta ziyadar, munis birer manzara olurlar.\\n\\n\u0130kinci k\xe2r: Cennet gibi bir fiyat veriliyor.\\n\\n\xdc\xe7\xfcnc\xfc k\xe2r: Her aza ve h\xe2sselerin k\u0131ymeti, birden bine \xe7\u0131kar.\\n\\nMesela, ak\u0131l bir \xe2lettir. E\u011fer Cenab-\u0131 Hakk\u2019a satmay\u0131p belki nefis hesab\u0131na \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rsan \xf6yle me\u015f\u2019um ve m\xfcz\u2019i\xe7 ve muacciz bir \xe2let olur ki ge\xe7mi\u015f zaman\u0131n \xe2l\xe2m-\u0131 haz\xeenanesini ve gelecek zaman\u0131n ehval-i muhavvifanesini senin bu b\xee\xe7are ba\u015f\u0131na y\xfckletecek, y\xfcm\xfcns\xfcz ve muz\u0131r bir \xe2let derekesine iner. \u0130\u015fte bunun i\xe7indir ki f\xe2s\u0131k adam, akl\u0131n iz\u2019a\xe7 ve tacizinden kurtulmak i\xe7in galiben ya sarho\u015flu\u011fa veya e\u011flenceye ka\xe7ar. E\u011fer M\xe2lik-i Hakiki\u2019sine sat\u0131lsa ve onun hesab\u0131na \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rsan ak\u0131l, \xf6yle t\u0131ls\u0131ml\u0131 bir anahtar olur ki \u015fu k\xe2inatta olan nihayetsiz rahmet hazinelerini ve hikmet definelerini a\xe7ar. Ve bununla sahibini, saadet-i ebediyeye m\xfcheyya eden bir m\xfcr\u015fid-i Rabban\xee derecesine \xe7\u0131kar.\\n\\nMesela, g\xf6z bir h\xe2ssedir ki ruh bu \xe2lemi o pencere ile seyreder. E\u011fer Cenab-\u0131 Hakk\u2019a satmay\u0131p belki nefis hesab\u0131na \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rsan ge\xe7ici, devams\u0131z baz\u0131 g\xfczellikleri, manzaralar\u0131 seyir ile \u015fehvet ve heves-i nefsaniyeye bir kavvad derekesinde bir hizmetk\xe2r olur. E\u011fer g\xf6z\xfc, g\xf6z\xfcn S\xe2ni\u2019-i Bas\xeer\u2019ine satsan ve onun hesab\u0131na ve izni dairesinde \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rsan o zaman \u015fu g\xf6z, \u015fu kitab-\u0131 kebir-i k\xe2inat\u0131n bir m\xfctalaac\u0131s\u0131 ve \u015fu \xe2lemdeki mu\u2019cizat-\u0131 sanat-\u0131 Rabbaniyenin bir seyircisi ve \u015fu k\xfcre-i arz bah\xe7esindeki rahmet \xe7i\xe7eklerinin m\xfcbarek bir ar\u0131s\u0131 derecesine \xe7\u0131kar.\\n\\nMesela, dildeki kuvve-i zaikay\u0131, F\xe2t\u0131r-\u0131 Hak\xeem\u2019ine satmazsan belki nefis hesab\u0131na, mide nam\u0131na \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rsan o vakit midenin tavlas\u0131na ve fabrikas\u0131na bir kap\u0131c\u0131 derekesine iner, sukut eder. E\u011fer Rezzak-\u0131 Ker\xeem\u2019e satsan o zaman dildeki kuvve-i zaika, rahmet-i \u0130lahiye hazinelerinin bir n\xe2z\u0131r-\u0131 mahiri ve kudret-i Samedaniye matbahlar\u0131n\u0131n bir m\xfcfetti\u015f-i \u015f\xe2kiri r\xfctbesine \xe7\u0131kar.\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte ey ak\u0131l, dikkat et! Me\u015f\u2019um bir \xe2let nerede, k\xe2inat anahtar\u0131 nerede? Ey g\xf6z, g\xfczel bak! \xc2di bir kavvad nerede, k\xfct\xfcphane-i \u0130lah\xeenin m\xfctefennin bir n\xe2z\u0131r\u0131 nerede? Ve ey dil, iyi tat! Bir tavla kap\u0131c\u0131s\u0131 ve bir fabrika yasak\xe7\u0131s\u0131 nerede, hazine-i h\xe2ssa-i rahmet n\xe2z\u0131r\u0131 nerede?\\n\\nVe daha bunlar gibi ba\u015fka \xe2letleri ve azalar\u0131 k\u0131yas etsen anlars\u0131n ki hakikaten m\xfc\u2019min cennete l\xe2y\u0131k ve k\xe2fir cehenneme muvaf\u0131k bir mahiyet kesbeder. Ve onlar\u0131n her biri, \xf6yle bir k\u0131ymet almalar\u0131n\u0131n sebebi; m\xfc\u2019min, iman\u0131yla H\xe2l\u0131k\u2019\u0131n\u0131n emanetini, onun nam\u0131na ve izni dairesinde istimal etmesidir. Ve k\xe2fir, h\u0131yanet edip nefs-i emmare hesab\u0131na \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rmas\u0131d\u0131r.\\n\\nD\xf6rd\xfcnc\xfc k\xe2r: \u0130nsan zay\u0131ft\u0131r, belalar\u0131 \xe7ok. Fakirdir, ihtiyac\u0131 pek ziyade. \xc2cizdir, hayat y\xfck\xfc pek a\u011f\u0131r. E\u011fer Kad\xeer-i Z\xfclcelal\u2019e dayan\u0131p tevekk\xfcl etmezse ve itimat edip teslim olmazsa, vicdan\u0131 daim azap i\xe7inde kal\u0131r. Semeresiz me\u015fakkatler, elemler, teess\xfcfler onu bo\u011far; ya sarho\u015f veya canavar eder.\\n\\nBe\u015finci k\xe2r: B\xfct\xfcn o aza ve \xe2letlerin ibadeti ve tesbihat\u0131 ve o y\xfcksek \xfccretleri, en muhta\xe7 oldu\u011fun bir zamanda, cennet yemi\u015fleri suretinde sana verilece\u011fine ehl-i zevk ve ke\u015fif ve ehl-i ihtisas ve m\xfc\u015fahede ittifak etmi\u015fler.\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte bu be\u015f mertebe k\xe2rl\u0131 ticareti yapmazsan \u015fu k\xe2rlardan mahrumiyetten ba\u015fka, be\u015f derece hasaret i\xe7inde hasarete d\xfc\u015feceksin.\\n\\nBirinci hasaret: O kadar sevdi\u011fin mal ve evlat ve peresti\u015f etti\u011fin nefis ve heva ve meftun oldu\u011fun gen\xe7lik ve hayat zayi olup kaybolacak, senin elinden \xe7\u0131kacaklar. Fakat g\xfcnahlar\u0131n\u0131, elemlerini sana b\u0131rak\u0131p boynuna y\xfckletecekler.\\n\\n\u0130kinci hasaret: Emanette h\u0131yanet cezas\u0131n\u0131 \xe7ekeceksin. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc en k\u0131ymettar \xe2letleri, en k\u0131ymetsiz \u015feylerde sarf edip nefsine zulmettin.\",\"modernText\":\"**Birinci k\xe2r:** [[ge\xe7ici|f\xe2ni|]] mal, [[ebediyet kazan\u0131r|beka bulur|sonsuzluk kazan\u0131r, kal\u0131c\u0131 hale gelir]]. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc [[Varl\u0131\u011f\u0131 sonsuz olan|Kayyum-u B\xe2ki|Varl\u0131\u011f\u0131 kendinden olup her \u015feye hayat ve devaml\u0131l\u0131k veren Allah]] olan [[Y\xfccelik sahibi olan Allah'a|Zat-\u0131 Z\xfclcelal\u2019e|Azamet ve celal sahibi olan Allah'\u0131n zat\u0131na]] verilen ve onun yolunda [[harcanan|sarf edilen|]] \u015fu [[ge\xe7ip giden \xf6m\xfcr|\xf6mr-\xfc z\xe2il|t\xfckenmeye mahkum olan ge\xe7ici hayat]], [[sonsuza|b\xe2kiye|kal\u0131c\u0131 ve ebedi olana]] [[d\xf6n\xfc\u015f\xfcr|ink\u0131lab eder|]], [[kal\u0131c\u0131|b\xe2ki|sonsuz, t\xfckenmez]] meyveler verir. O vakit \xf6m\xfcr dakikalar\u0131, \xe2deta tohumlar, \xe7ekirdekler [[konumunda|h\xfckm\xfcnde|niteli\u011finde, yerinde]] [[g\xf6r\xfcn\xfc\u015fte|zahiren|]] [[yok olur|fena bulur|son bulur, silinip gider]], \xe7\xfcr\xfcr. Fakat [[sonsuzluk aleminde|\xe2lem-i bekada|ahiret yurdunda, kal\u0131c\u0131 olan d\xfcnyada]], [[mutluluk|saadet|]] \xe7i\xe7ekleri a\xe7arlar ve s\xfcmb\xfcllenirler. Ve [[kabir aleminde|\xe2lem-i berzahta|\xf6l\xfcm ile k\u0131yamet aras\u0131ndaki bekleme yerinde]] [[\u0131\u015f\u0131kl\u0131|ziyadar|nurlu, ayd\u0131nl\u0131k]], [[cana yak\u0131n|munis|sevimli, huzur veren]] birer manzara olurlar.\\n\\n**\u0130kinci k\xe2r:** Cennet gibi bir fiyat veriliyor.\\n\\n**\xdc\xe7\xfcnc\xfc k\xe2r:** Her [[organlar|aza|]] ve [[duygular\u0131n|h\xe2sselerin|yeteneklerin, cihazlar\u0131n (g\xf6z, kulak gibi)]] k\u0131ymeti, birden bine \xe7\u0131kar.\\n\\nMesela, ak\u0131l bir \xe2lettir. E\u011fer [[Y\xfcce Allah'a|Cenab-\u0131 Hakk\u2019a|]] satmay\u0131p belki [[\xf6z benlik|nefis|insan\u0131n bencil ve s\xfcfli arzular\u0131]] hesab\u0131na \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rsan \xf6yle [[u\u011fursuz|me\u015f\u2019um|]] ve [[s\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131 veren|m\xfcz\u2019i\xe7|rahats\u0131z edici, huzur ka\xe7\u0131ran]] ve [[b\u0131kt\u0131ran|muacciz|usand\u0131ran, aciz b\u0131rakan]] bir \xe2let olur ki ge\xe7mi\u015f zaman\u0131n [[h\xfcz\xfcnl\xfc elemlerini|\xe2l\xe2m-\u0131 haz\xeenanesini|ge\xe7mi\u015fin keder verici ac\u0131lar\u0131n\u0131]] ve gelecek zaman\u0131n [[korkun\xe7 hallerini|ehval-i muhavvifanesini|gelece\u011fin korku veren deh\u015fetli olaylar\u0131n\u0131]] senin bu [[\xe7aresiz|b\xee\xe7are|]] ba\u015f\u0131na y\xfckletecek, [[u\u011fursuz|y\xfcm\xfcns\xfcz|bereketsiz]] ve [[zararl\u0131|muz\u0131r|]] bir \xe2let [[a\u015fa\u011f\u0131l\u0131k seviyesine d\xfc\u015fer|derekesine iner|\xe7ukuruna d\xfc\u015fer, en alt mertebesine iner]]. \u0130\u015fte bunun i\xe7indir ki [[g\xfcnahk\xe2r|f\xe2s\u0131k|Allah'\u0131n emirlerine kar\u015f\u0131 gelip yoldan \xe7\u0131kan]] adam, akl\u0131n [[rahats\u0131z etme|iz\u2019a\xe7|]] ve [[rahats\u0131zl\u0131\u011f\u0131ndan|tacizinden|bask\u0131s\u0131ndan, tedirgin etmesinden]] kurtulmak i\xe7in [[\xe7o\u011funlukla|galiben|]] ya sarho\u015flu\u011fa veya e\u011flenceye ka\xe7ar. E\u011fer [[Ger\xe7ek sahibine|M\xe2lik-i Hakiki\u2019sine|Her \u015feyin tek ve as\u0131l sahibi olan Allah'a]] sat\u0131lsa ve onun hesab\u0131na \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rsan ak\u0131l, \xf6yle t\u0131ls\u0131ml\u0131 bir anahtar olur ki \u015fu k\xe2inatta olan [[sonsuz|nihayetsiz|]] rahmet hazinelerini ve [[faydal\u0131 ama\xe7|hikmet|her \u015feyin arkas\u0131ndaki gizli gaye ve nizam]] definelerini a\xe7ar. Ve bununla sahibini, [[ebedi mutlulu\u011fa|saadet-i ebediyeye|]] [[haz\u0131rlayan|m\xfcheyya eden|]] bir [[Allah'\u0131 tan\u0131tan rehber|m\xfcr\u015fid-i Rabban\xee|insan\u0131 Allah'a ula\u015ft\u0131ran ilahi yol g\xf6sterici]] derecesine \xe7\u0131kar.\\n\\nMesela, g\xf6z bir [[duygudur|h\xe2ssedir|organd\u0131r, yetenektir]] ki ruh bu \xe2lemi o pencere ile seyreder. E\u011fer [[Y\xfcce Allah'a|Cenab-\u0131 Hakk\u2019a|]] satmay\u0131p belki [[\xf6z benlik|nefis|]] hesab\u0131na \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rsan ge\xe7ici, devams\u0131z baz\u0131 g\xfczellikleri, manzaralar\u0131 seyir ile \u015fehvet ve [[nefsin ge\xe7ici arzular\u0131na|heves-i nefsaniyeye|]] bir [[k\xf6t\xfc yola d\xfc\u015f\xfcren|kavvad|gayrime\u015fru i\u015flere arac\u0131l\u0131k eden]] [[a\u015fa\u011f\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131nda|derekesinde|\xe7ukurunda, seviyesinde]] bir hizmetk\xe2r olur. E\u011fer g\xf6z\xfc, g\xf6z\xfcn [[Her \u015feyi g\xf6r\xfcp yaratan Sanatkar\u0131na|S\xe2ni\u2019-i Bas\xeer\u2019ine|Her \u015feyi kemaliyle g\xf6ren ve her \u015feyi sanatla var eden Allah'a]] satsan ve onun hesab\u0131na ve izni dairesinde \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rsan o zaman \u015fu g\xf6z, \u015fu [[k\xe2inat adl\u0131 b\xfcy\xfck kitab\u0131n|kitab-\u0131 kebir-i k\xe2inat\u0131n|evrenin bir kitap gibi okunmas\u0131 gereken geni\u015f y\xfcz\xfc]] bir [[okuyucusu|m\xfctalaac\u0131s\u0131|dikkatle inceleyeni]] ve \u015fu \xe2lemdeki [[ilahi sanat mucizelerinin|mu\u2019cizat-\u0131 sanat-\u0131 Rabbaniyenin|Allah'\u0131n harika ve taklit edilemez sanat eserlerinin]] bir seyircisi ve \u015fu [[yerk\xfcre|k\xfcre-i arz|]] bah\xe7esindeki rahmet \xe7i\xe7eklerinin m\xfcbarek bir ar\u0131s\u0131 derecesine \xe7\u0131kar.\\n\\nMesela, dildeki [[tatma duygusunu|kuvve-i zaikay\u0131|]], [[Hikmetle yaratan Yarat\u0131c\u0131s\u0131na|F\xe2t\u0131r-\u0131 Hak\xeem\u2019ine|Her \u015feyi hikmetle ve yoktan var eden Allah'a]] satmazsan belki [[\xf6z benlik|nefis|]] hesab\u0131na, mide nam\u0131na \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rsan o vakit midenin tavlas\u0131na ve fabrikas\u0131na bir kap\u0131c\u0131 [[a\u015fa\u011f\u0131l\u0131k seviyesine d\xfc\u015fer|derekesine iner|]], [[al\xe7al\u0131r|sukut eder|d\xfc\u015fer]]. E\u011fer [[C\xf6mert\xe7e r\u0131z\u0131k verene|Rezzak-\u0131 Ker\xeem\u2019e|\u0130kram\u0131 bol olan ve her canl\u0131y\u0131 besleyen Allah'a]] satsan o zaman dildeki [[tatma duygusu|kuvve-i zaika|]], [[Allah'\u0131n rahmeti|rahmet-i \u0130lahiye|]] hazinelerinin bir [[becerikli bakan\u0131|n\xe2z\u0131r-\u0131 mahiri|i\u015finin ehli olan m\xfcfetti\u015fi ve g\xf6zlemcisi]] ve [[Allah'\u0131n sonsuz g\xfcc\xfc|kudret-i Samedaniye|Hi\xe7bir \u015feye muhta\xe7 olmayan Allah'\u0131n her \u015feyi yaratan kudreti]] [[mutfaklar\u0131n\u0131n|matbahlar\u0131n\u0131n|]] bir [[\u015f\xfckreden denetleyicisi|m\xfcfetti\u015f-i \u015f\xe2kiri|]] r\xfctbesine \xe7\u0131kar.\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte ey ak\u0131l, dikkat et! [[U\u011fursuz|Me\u015f\u2019um|]] bir \xe2let nerede, k\xe2inat anahtar\u0131 nerede? Ey g\xf6z, g\xfczel bak! [[A\u015fa\u011f\u0131l\u0131k|\xc2di|Basit, k\u0131ymetsiz]] bir [[k\xf6t\xfc yola d\xfc\u015f\xfcren|kavvad|]] nerede, [[\u0130lahi k\xfct\xfcphanenin|k\xfct\xfcphane-i \u0130lah\xeenin|Allah'\u0131n ilmiyle yaz\u0131lm\u0131\u015f olan k\xe2inat\u0131n]] [[fen ve bilim sahibi|m\xfctefennin|ilimli, uzman]] bir [[bakan\u0131|n\xe2z\u0131r\u0131|denetleyicisi, g\xf6zlemcisi]] nerede? Ve ey dil, iyi tat! Bir tavla kap\u0131c\u0131s\u0131 ve bir fabrika yasak\xe7\u0131s\u0131 nerede, [[\xf6zel rahmet hazinesi|hazine-i h\xe2ssa-i rahmet|Allah'\u0131n rahmetinin en \xf6zel ve k\u0131ymetli hazinesi]] [[bakan\u0131|n\xe2z\u0131r\u0131|]] nerede?\\n\\nVe daha bunlar gibi ba\u015fka \xe2letleri ve [[organlar\u0131|azalar\u0131|]] k\u0131yas etsen anlars\u0131n ki hakikaten [[inanan|m\xfc\u2019min|]] cennete l\xe2y\u0131k ve k\xe2fir cehenneme [[uygun|muvaf\u0131k|]] bir [[i\xe7 y\xfcz|mahiyet|karakter, yarat\u0131l\u0131\u015f \xf6zelli\u011fi]] [[kazan\u0131r|kesbeder|]]. Ve onlar\u0131n her biri, \xf6yle bir k\u0131ymet almalar\u0131n\u0131n sebebi; [[inanan|m\xfc\u2019min|]], iman\u0131yla [[Yarat\u0131c\u0131s\u0131n\u0131n|H\xe2l\u0131k\u2019\u0131n\u0131n|]] emanetini, onun nam\u0131na ve izni dairesinde [[kullanmas\u0131d\u0131r|istimal etmesidir|]]. Ve k\xe2fir, [[hainlik edip|h\u0131yanet edip|emanete zarar verip]] [[k\xf6t\xfcl\xfc\u011f\xfc emreden nefis|nefs-i emmare|insan\u0131 s\xfcrekli g\xfcnaha ve bencil arzulara s\xfcr\xfckleyen i\xe7 benlik]] hesab\u0131na \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rmas\u0131d\u0131r.\\n\\n**D\xf6rd\xfcnc\xfc k\xe2r:** \u0130nsan zay\u0131ft\u0131r, belalar\u0131 \xe7ok. Fakirdir, ihtiyac\u0131 pek ziyade. \xc2cizdir, hayat y\xfck\xfc pek a\u011f\u0131r. E\u011fer [[Sonsuz g\xfc\xe7 sahibi Allah'a|Kad\xeer-i Z\xfclcelal\u2019e|]] dayan\u0131p [[g\xfcvenip dayanmazsa|tevekk\xfcl etmezse|]] ve itimat edip [[boyun e\u011fip raz\u0131 olmazsa|teslim olmazsa|]], vicdan\u0131 [[s\xfcrekli|daim|]] azap i\xe7inde kal\u0131r. [[Meyvesiz|Semeresiz|Sonu\xe7suz, faydas\u0131z]] [[zorluklar|me\u015fakkatler|]], elemler, [[\xfcz\xfcnt\xfcler|teess\xfcfler|pi\u015fmanl\u0131klar ve kederler]] onu bo\u011far; ya sarho\u015f veya canavar eder.\\n\\n**Be\u015finci k\xe2r:** B\xfct\xfcn o [[organlar|aza|]] ve \xe2letlerin ibadeti ve [[zikirleri|tesbihat\u0131|Allah'\u0131 an\u0131p y\xfcceltmeleri]] ve o y\xfcksek \xfccretleri, en muhta\xe7 oldu\u011fun bir zamanda, cennet yemi\u015fleri suretinde sana verilece\u011fine [[kalp g\xf6z\xfc a\xe7\u0131k olanlar|ehl-i zevk ve ke\u015fif|manevi hakikatleri bizzat tadan ve g\xf6ren veliler]] ve [[uzmanlar|ehl-i ihtisas|]] ve [[g\xf6zlem|m\xfc\u015fahede|]] [[s\xf6z birli\u011fi etmi\u015fler|ittifak etmi\u015fler|ayn\u0131 fikirde birle\u015fmi\u015fler]].\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte bu be\u015f [[seviye|mertebe|derece]] k\xe2rl\u0131 ticareti yapmazsan \u015fu k\xe2rlardan mahrumiyetten ba\u015fka, be\u015f derece [[ziyan|hasaret|kay\u0131p, zarar]] i\xe7inde [[ziyana|hasarete|]] d\xfc\u015feceksin.\\n\\n**Birinci [[ziyan|hasaret|]]:** O kadar sevdi\u011fin mal ve evlat ve [[taparcas\u0131na sevdi\u011fin|peresti\u015f etti\u011fin|]] [[\xf6z benlik|nefis|]] ve [[nefsani arzular|heva|bo\u015f ve ge\xe7ici hevesler]] ve [[tutkuyla ba\u011fland\u0131\u011f\u0131n|meftun oldu\u011fun|hayran\u0131 oldu\u011fun]] gen\xe7lik ve hayat [[kaybolup|zayi olup|bo\u015fa gidip]] kaybolacak, senin elinden \xe7\u0131kacaklar. Fakat g\xfcnahlar\u0131n\u0131, elemlerini sana b\u0131rak\u0131p boynuna y\xfckletecekler.\\n\\n**\u0130kinci [[ziyan|hasaret|]]:** Emanette [[hainlik|h\u0131yanet|]] cezas\u0131n\u0131 \xe7ekeceksin. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc en k\u0131ymettar \xe2letleri, en k\u0131ymetsiz \u015feylerde [[harcay\u0131p|sarf edip|]] nefsine zulmettin.\",\"processedBy\":\"\ud83e\udde0 Gemini 3.0 Pro (Web - Manuel) on 2025.12.17-18:17\",\"lastUpdated\":\"2025-12-17T15:26:35.688Z\",\"oldText\":\"**Birinci k\xe2r:** [[f\xe2ni|ge\xe7ici]] mal, [[beka bulur|ebediyet kazan\u0131r|sonsuzluk kazan\u0131r, kal\u0131c\u0131 hale gelir]]. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc [[Kayyum-u B\xe2ki|Varl\u0131\u011f\u0131 sonsuz olan|Varl\u0131\u011f\u0131 kendinden olup her \u015feye hayat ve devaml\u0131l\u0131k veren Allah]] olan [[Zat-\u0131 Z\xfclcelal\u2019e|Y\xfccelik sahibi olan Allah'a|Azamet ve celal sahibi olan Allah'\u0131n zat\u0131na]] verilen ve onun yolunda [[sarf edilen|harcanan]] \u015fu [[\xf6mr-\xfc z\xe2il|ge\xe7ip giden \xf6m\xfcr|t\xfckenmeye mahkum olan ge\xe7ici hayat]], [[b\xe2kiye|sonsuza|kal\u0131c\u0131 ve ebedi olana]] [[ink\u0131lab eder|d\xf6n\xfc\u015f\xfcr]], [[b\xe2ki|kal\u0131c\u0131|sonsuz, t\xfckenmez]] meyveler verir. O vakit \xf6m\xfcr dakikalar\u0131, \xe2deta tohumlar, \xe7ekirdekler [[h\xfckm\xfcnde|konumunda|niteli\u011finde, yerinde]] [[zahiren|g\xf6r\xfcn\xfc\u015fte]] [[fena bulur|yok olur|son bulur, silinip gider]], \xe7\xfcr\xfcr. Fakat [[\xe2lem-i bekada|sonsuzluk aleminde|ahiret yurdunda, kal\u0131c\u0131 olan d\xfcnyada]], [[saadet|mutluluk]] \xe7i\xe7ekleri a\xe7arlar ve s\xfcmb\xfcllenirler. Ve [[\xe2lem-i berzahta|kabir aleminde|\xf6l\xfcm ile k\u0131yamet aras\u0131ndaki bekleme yerinde]] [[ziyadar|\u0131\u015f\u0131kl\u0131|nurlu, ayd\u0131nl\u0131k]], [[munis|cana yak\u0131n|sevimli, huzur veren]] birer manzara olurlar.\\n\\n**\u0130kinci k\xe2r:** Cennet gibi bir fiyat veriliyor.\\n\\n**\xdc\xe7\xfcnc\xfc k\xe2r:** Her [[aza|organlar]] ve [[h\xe2sselerin|duygular\u0131n|yeteneklerin, cihazlar\u0131n (g\xf6z, kulak gibi)]] k\u0131ymeti, birden bine \xe7\u0131kar.\\n\\nMesela, ak\u0131l bir \xe2lettir. E\u011fer [[Cenab-\u0131 Hakk\u2019a|Y\xfcce Allah'a]] satmay\u0131p belki [[nefis|\xf6z benlik|insan\u0131n bencil ve s\xfcfli arzular\u0131]] hesab\u0131na \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rsan \xf6yle [[me\u015f\u2019um|u\u011fursuz]] ve [[m\xfcz\u2019i\xe7|s\u0131k\u0131nt\u0131 veren|rahats\u0131z edici, huzur ka\xe7\u0131ran]] ve [[muacciz|b\u0131kt\u0131ran|usand\u0131ran, aciz b\u0131rakan]] bir \xe2let olur ki ge\xe7mi\u015f zaman\u0131n [[\xe2l\xe2m-\u0131 haz\xeenanesini|h\xfcz\xfcnl\xfc elemlerini|ge\xe7mi\u015fin keder verici ac\u0131lar\u0131n\u0131]] ve gelecek zaman\u0131n [[ehval-i muhavvifanesini|korkun\xe7 hallerini|gelece\u011fin korku veren deh\u015fetli olaylar\u0131n\u0131]] senin bu [[b\xee\xe7are|\xe7aresiz]] ba\u015f\u0131na y\xfckletecek, [[y\xfcm\xfcns\xfcz|u\u011fursuz|bereketsiz]] ve [[muz\u0131r|zararl\u0131]] bir \xe2let [[derekesine iner|a\u015fa\u011f\u0131l\u0131k seviyesine d\xfc\u015fer|\xe7ukuruna d\xfc\u015fer, en alt mertebesine iner]]. \u0130\u015fte bunun i\xe7indir ki [[f\xe2s\u0131k|g\xfcnahk\xe2r|Allah'\u0131n emirlerine kar\u015f\u0131 gelip yoldan \xe7\u0131kan]] adam, akl\u0131n [[iz\u2019a\xe7|rahats\u0131z etme]] ve [[tacizinden|rahats\u0131zl\u0131\u011f\u0131ndan|bask\u0131s\u0131ndan, tedirgin etmesinden]] kurtulmak i\xe7in [[galiben|\xe7o\u011funlukla]] ya sarho\u015flu\u011fa veya e\u011flenceye ka\xe7ar. E\u011fer [[M\xe2lik-i Hakiki\u2019sine|Ger\xe7ek sahibine|Her \u015feyin tek ve as\u0131l sahibi olan Allah'a]] sat\u0131lsa ve onun hesab\u0131na \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rsan ak\u0131l, \xf6yle t\u0131ls\u0131ml\u0131 bir anahtar olur ki \u015fu k\xe2inatta olan [[nihayetsiz|sonsuz]] rahmet hazinelerini ve [[hikmet|faydal\u0131 ama\xe7|her \u015feyin arkas\u0131ndaki gizli gaye ve nizam]] definelerini a\xe7ar. Ve bununla sahibini, [[saadet-i ebediyeye|ebedi mutlulu\u011fa]] [[m\xfcheyya eden|haz\u0131rlayan]] bir [[m\xfcr\u015fid-i Rabban\xee|Allah'\u0131 tan\u0131tan rehber|insan\u0131 Allah'a ula\u015ft\u0131ran ilahi yol g\xf6sterici]] derecesine \xe7\u0131kar.\\n\\nMesela, g\xf6z bir [[h\xe2ssedir|duygudur|organd\u0131r, yetenektir]] ki ruh bu \xe2lemi o pencere ile seyreder. E\u011fer [[Cenab-\u0131 Hakk\u2019a|Y\xfcce Allah'a]] satmay\u0131p belki [[nefis|\xf6z benlik]] hesab\u0131na \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rsan ge\xe7ici, devams\u0131z baz\u0131 g\xfczellikleri, manzaralar\u0131 seyir ile \u015fehvet ve [[heves-i nefsaniyeye|nefsin ge\xe7ici arzular\u0131na]] bir [[kavvad|k\xf6t\xfc yola d\xfc\u015f\xfcren|gayrime\u015fru i\u015flere arac\u0131l\u0131k eden]] [[derekesinde|a\u015fa\u011f\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131nda|\xe7ukurunda, seviyesinde]] bir hizmetk\xe2r olur. E\u011fer g\xf6z\xfc, g\xf6z\xfcn [[S\xe2ni\u2019-i Bas\xeer\u2019ine|Her \u015feyi g\xf6r\xfcp yaratan Sanatkar\u0131na|Her \u015feyi kemaliyle g\xf6ren ve her \u015feyi sanatla var eden Allah'a]] satsan ve onun hesab\u0131na ve izni dairesinde \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rsan o zaman \u015fu g\xf6z, \u015fu [[kitab-\u0131 kebir-i k\xe2inat\u0131n|k\xe2inat adl\u0131 b\xfcy\xfck kitab\u0131n|evrenin bir kitap gibi okunmas\u0131 gereken geni\u015f y\xfcz\xfc]] bir [[m\xfctalaac\u0131s\u0131|okuyucusu|dikkatle inceleyeni]] ve \u015fu \xe2lemdeki [[mu\u2019cizat-\u0131 sanat-\u0131 Rabbaniyenin|ilahi sanat mucizelerinin|Allah'\u0131n harika ve taklit edilemez sanat eserlerinin]] bir seyircisi ve \u015fu [[k\xfcre-i arz|yerk\xfcre]] bah\xe7esindeki rahmet \xe7i\xe7eklerinin m\xfcbarek bir ar\u0131s\u0131 derecesine \xe7\u0131kar.\\n\\nMesela, dildeki [[kuvve-i zaikay\u0131|tatma duygusunu]], [[F\xe2t\u0131r-\u0131 Hak\xeem\u2019ine|Hikmetle yaratan Yarat\u0131c\u0131s\u0131na|Her \u015feyi hikmetle ve yoktan var eden Allah'a]] satmazsan belki [[nefis|\xf6z benlik]] hesab\u0131na, mide nam\u0131na \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rsan o vakit midenin tavlas\u0131na ve fabrikas\u0131na bir kap\u0131c\u0131 [[derekesine iner|a\u015fa\u011f\u0131l\u0131k seviyesine d\xfc\u015fer]], [[sukut eder|al\xe7al\u0131r|d\xfc\u015fer]]. E\u011fer [[Rezzak-\u0131 Ker\xeem\u2019e|C\xf6mert\xe7e r\u0131z\u0131k verene|\u0130kram\u0131 bol olan ve her canl\u0131y\u0131 besleyen Allah'a]] satsan o zaman dildeki [[kuvve-i zaika|tatma duygusu]], [[rahmet-i \u0130lahiye|Allah'\u0131n rahmeti]] hazinelerinin bir [[n\xe2z\u0131r-\u0131 mahiri|becerikli bakan\u0131|i\u015finin ehli olan m\xfcfetti\u015fi ve g\xf6zlemcisi]] ve [[kudret-i Samedaniye|Allah'\u0131n sonsuz g\xfcc\xfc|Hi\xe7bir \u015feye muhta\xe7 olmayan Allah'\u0131n her \u015feyi yaratan kudreti]] [[matbahlar\u0131n\u0131n|mutfaklar\u0131n\u0131n]] bir [[m\xfcfetti\u015f-i \u015f\xe2kiri|\u015f\xfckreden denetleyicisi]] r\xfctbesine \xe7\u0131kar.\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte ey ak\u0131l, dikkat et! [[Me\u015f\u2019um|U\u011fursuz]] bir \xe2let nerede, k\xe2inat anahtar\u0131 nerede? Ey g\xf6z, g\xfczel bak! [[\xc2di|A\u015fa\u011f\u0131l\u0131k|Basit, k\u0131ymetsiz]] bir [[kavvad|k\xf6t\xfc yola d\xfc\u015f\xfcren]] nerede, [[k\xfct\xfcphane-i \u0130lah\xeenin|\u0130lahi k\xfct\xfcphanenin|Allah'\u0131n ilmiyle yaz\u0131lm\u0131\u015f olan k\xe2inat\u0131n]] [[m\xfctefennin|fen ve bilim sahibi|ilimli, uzman]] bir [[n\xe2z\u0131r\u0131|bakan\u0131|denetleyicisi, g\xf6zlemcisi]] nerede? Ve ey dil, iyi tat! Bir tavla kap\u0131c\u0131s\u0131 ve bir fabrika yasak\xe7\u0131s\u0131 nerede, [[hazine-i h\xe2ssa-i rahmet|\xf6zel rahmet hazinesi|Allah'\u0131n rahmetinin en \xf6zel ve k\u0131ymetli hazinesi]] [[n\xe2z\u0131r\u0131|bakan\u0131]] nerede?\\n\\nVe daha bunlar gibi ba\u015fka \xe2letleri ve [[azalar\u0131|organlar\u0131]] k\u0131yas etsen anlars\u0131n ki hakikaten [[m\xfc\u2019min|inanan]] cennete l\xe2y\u0131k ve k\xe2fir cehenneme [[muvaf\u0131k|uygun]] bir [[mahiyet|i\xe7 y\xfcz|karakter, yarat\u0131l\u0131\u015f \xf6zelli\u011fi]] [[kesbeder|kazan\u0131r]]. Ve onlar\u0131n her biri, \xf6yle bir k\u0131ymet almalar\u0131n\u0131n sebebi; [[m\xfc\u2019min|inanan]], iman\u0131yla [[H\xe2l\u0131k\u2019\u0131n\u0131n|Yarat\u0131c\u0131s\u0131n\u0131n]] emanetini, onun nam\u0131na ve izni dairesinde [[istimal etmesidir|kullanmas\u0131d\u0131r]]. Ve k\xe2fir, [[h\u0131yanet edip|hainlik edip|emanete zarar verip]] [[nefs-i emmare|k\xf6t\xfcl\xfc\u011f\xfc emreden nefis|insan\u0131 s\xfcrekli g\xfcnaha ve bencil arzulara s\xfcr\xfckleyen i\xe7 benlik]] hesab\u0131na \xe7al\u0131\u015ft\u0131rmas\u0131d\u0131r.\\n\\n**D\xf6rd\xfcnc\xfc k\xe2r:** \u0130nsan zay\u0131ft\u0131r, belalar\u0131 \xe7ok. Fakirdir, ihtiyac\u0131 pek ziyade. \xc2cizdir, hayat y\xfck\xfc pek a\u011f\u0131r. E\u011fer [[Kad\xeer-i Z\xfclcelal\u2019e|Sonsuz g\xfc\xe7 sahibi Allah'a]] dayan\u0131p [[tevekk\xfcl etmezse|g\xfcvenip dayanmazsa]] ve itimat edip [[teslim olmazsa|boyun e\u011fip raz\u0131 olmazsa]], vicdan\u0131 [[daim|s\xfcrekli]] azap i\xe7inde kal\u0131r. [[Semeresiz|Meyvesiz|Sonu\xe7suz, faydas\u0131z]] [[me\u015fakkatler|zorluklar]], elemler, [[teess\xfcfler|\xfcz\xfcnt\xfcler|pi\u015fmanl\u0131klar ve kederler]] onu bo\u011far; ya sarho\u015f veya canavar eder.\\n\\n**Be\u015finci k\xe2r:** B\xfct\xfcn o [[aza|organlar]] ve \xe2letlerin ibadeti ve [[tesbihat\u0131|zikirleri|Allah'\u0131 an\u0131p y\xfcceltmeleri]] ve o y\xfcksek \xfccretleri, en muhta\xe7 oldu\u011fun bir zamanda, cennet yemi\u015fleri suretinde sana verilece\u011fine [[ehl-i zevk ve ke\u015fif|kalp g\xf6z\xfc a\xe7\u0131k olanlar|manevi hakikatleri bizzat tadan ve g\xf6ren veliler]] ve [[ehl-i ihtisas|uzmanlar]] ve [[m\xfc\u015fahede|g\xf6zlem]] [[ittifak etmi\u015fler|s\xf6z birli\u011fi etmi\u015fler|ayn\u0131 fikirde birle\u015fmi\u015fler]].\\n\\n\u0130\u015fte bu be\u015f [[mertebe|seviye|derece]] k\xe2rl\u0131 ticareti yapmazsan \u015fu k\xe2rlardan mahrumiyetten ba\u015fka, be\u015f derece [[hasaret|ziyan|kay\u0131p, zarar]] i\xe7inde [[hasarete|ziyana]] d\xfc\u015feceksin.\\n\\n**Birinci [[hasaret|ziyan]]:** O kadar sevdi\u011fin mal ve evlat ve [[peresti\u015f etti\u011fin|taparcas\u0131na sevdi\u011fin]] [[nefis|\xf6z benlik]] ve [[heva|nefsani arzular|bo\u015f ve ge\xe7ici hevesler]] ve [[meftun oldu\u011fun|tutkuyla ba\u011fland\u0131\u011f\u0131n|hayran\u0131 oldu\u011fun]] gen\xe7lik ve hayat [[zayi olup|kaybolup|bo\u015fa gidip]] kaybolacak, senin elinden \xe7\u0131kacaklar. Fakat g\xfcnahlar\u0131n\u0131, elemlerini sana b\u0131rak\u0131p boynuna y\xfckletecekler.\\n\\n**\u0130kinci [[hasaret|ziyan]]:** Emanette [[h\u0131yanet|hainlik]] cezas\u0131n\u0131 \xe7ekeceksin. \xc7\xfcnk\xfc en k\u0131ymettar \xe2letleri, en k\u0131ymetsiz \u015feylerde [[sarf edip|harcay\u0131p]] nefsine zulmettin.\"},{\"pageId\":3,\"rawText\":\"\xdc\xe7\xfcnc\xfc hasaret: B\xfct\xfcn o k\u0131ymettar cihazat-\u0131 insaniyeyi, hayvanl\u0131ktan \xe7ok a\u015fa\u011f\u0131 bir derekeye d\xfc\u015f\xfcr\xfcp hikmet-i \u0130lahiyeye iftira ve zulmettin.\\n\\nD\xf6rd\xfcnc\xfc hasaret: Acz ve fakr\u0131n ile beraber, o pek a\u011f\u0131r hayat y\xfck\xfcn\xfc, zay\u0131f beline y\xfckleyip zeval ve firak sillesi alt\u0131nda daim vaveyl\xe2 edeceksin.\\n\\nBe\u015finci hasaret: Hayat-\u0131 ebediye esasat\u0131n\u0131 ve saadet-i uhreviye levaz\u0131mat\u0131n\u0131 tedarik etmek i\xe7in verilen ak\u0131l, kalp, g\xf6z ve dil gibi g\xfczel hediye-i Rahmaniyeyi, cehennem kap\u0131lar\u0131n\u0131 sana a\xe7acak \xe7irkin bir surete \xe7evirmektir.\\n\\n\u015eimdi satmaya bakaca\u011f\u0131z. Acaba o kadar a\u011f\u0131r bir \u015fey midir ki \xe7oklar\u0131 satmaktan ka\xe7\u0131yorlar. Yok, kat\u2019\xe2 ve asl\xe2! Hi\xe7 \xf6yle a\u011f\u0131rl\u0131\u011f\u0131 yoktur. Zira hel\xe2l dairesi geni\u015ftir, keyfe k\xe2fi gelir. Harama girmeye hi\xe7 l\xfczum yoktur. Feraiz-i \u0130lahiye ise hafiftir, azd\u0131r.\\n\\nAllah\u2019a abd ve asker olmak, \xf6yle lezzetli bir \u015fereftir ki tarif edilmez.\\n\\nVazife ise yaln\u0131z, bir asker gibi Allah nam\u0131na i\u015flemeli, ba\u015flamal\u0131. Ve Allah hesab\u0131yla vermeli ve almal\u0131. Ve izni ve kanunu dairesinde hareket etmeli, s\xfck\xfbnet bulmal\u0131.\\n\\nKusur etse isti\u011ffar etmeli. \u201cY\xe2 Rab! Kusurumuzu affet, bizi kendine kul kabul et, emanetini kabzetmek zaman\u0131na kadar bizi emanette emin k\u0131l, \xe2min!\u201d demeli ve ona yalvarmal\u0131.\\n\\n***\",\"modernText\":\"**\xdc\xe7\xfcnc\xfc [[zarar|hasaret|ziyan]]:** B\xfct\xfcn o [[de\u011ferli|k\u0131ymettar|k\u0131ymetli]] [[insani donan\u0131mlar\u0131|cihazat-\u0131 insaniyeyi|insana verilen duygu ve yetenekleri]], hayvanl\u0131ktan \xe7ok a\u015fa\u011f\u0131 bir [[a\u015fa\u011f\u0131 dereceye|derekeye|\xe7ukurun en dibine]] d\xfc\u015f\xfcr\xfcp [[Allah'\u0131n hikmetine|hikmet-i \u0130lahiyeye|Allah'\u0131n her \u015feyi yerli yerinde ve gayeli yaratmas\u0131na]] iftira ve [[haks\u0131zl\u0131k ettin|zulmettin|zul\xfcm yapt\u0131n]].\\n\\n**D\xf6rd\xfcnc\xfc [[zarar|hasaret|ziyan]]:** [[acizlik|Acz|g\xfc\xe7s\xfczl\xfck]] ve [[fakirli\u011fin|fakr\u0131n|ihtiya\xe7 i\xe7inde olu\u015fun]] ile beraber, o pek a\u011f\u0131r hayat y\xfck\xfcn\xfc, zay\u0131f beline y\xfckleyip [[sona erme|zeval|yok olu\u015f, bat\u0131\u015f]] ve [[ayr\u0131l\u0131k|firak|]] [[tokad\u0131|sillesi|]] alt\u0131nda [[daima|daim|s\xfcrekli]] [[feryat edeceksin|vaveyl\xe2 edeceksin|\xe7\u0131\u011fl\u0131k atacaks\u0131n]].\\n\\n**Be\u015finci [[zarar|hasaret|ziyan]]:** [[sonsuz hayat|Hayat-\u0131 ebediye|ahiret hayat\u0131]] [[temellerini|esasat\u0131n\u0131|esaslar\u0131n\u0131]] ve [[ahiret mutlulu\u011fu|saadet-i uhreviye|]] [[gere\xe7lerini|levaz\u0131mat\u0131n\u0131|malzemelerini, ihtiya\xe7lar\u0131n\u0131]] [[elde etmek|tedarik etmek|sa\u011flamak, haz\u0131rlamak]] i\xe7in verilen ak\u0131l, kalp, g\xf6z ve dil gibi g\xfczel [[Rahman olan Allah'\u0131n hediyesini|hediye-i Rahmaniyeyi|Merhametli Allah'\u0131n ba\u011f\u0131\u015f\u0131n\u0131]], cehennem kap\u0131lar\u0131n\u0131 sana a\xe7acak \xe7irkin bir [[bi\xe7ime|surete|\u015fekle, g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcme]] \xe7evirmektir.\\n\\n\u015eimdi satmaya bakaca\u011f\u0131z. Acaba o kadar a\u011f\u0131r bir \u015fey midir ki \xe7oklar\u0131 satmaktan ka\xe7\u0131yorlar. Yok, [[kesinlikle|kat\u2019\xe2|]] ve [[asla|asl\xe2|hi\xe7bir zaman]]! Hi\xe7 \xf6yle a\u011f\u0131rl\u0131\u011f\u0131 yoktur. [[\xe7\xfcnk\xfc|Zira|]] hel\xe2l dairesi geni\u015ftir, keyfe [[yeter|k\xe2fi gelir|yeterli gelir]]. Harama girmeye hi\xe7 [[gerek|l\xfczum|ihtiya\xe7]] yoktur. [[Allah'\u0131n farzlar\u0131|Feraiz-i \u0130lahiye|Allah'\u0131n emretti\u011fi zorunlu g\xf6revler]] ise hafiftir, azd\u0131r.\\n\\nAllah\u2019a [[kul|abd|k\xf6le]] ve asker olmak, \xf6yle lezzetli bir \u015fereftir ki tarif edilmez.\\n\\nVazife ise yaln\u0131z, bir asker gibi Allah [[ad\u0131na|nam\u0131na|]] i\u015flemeli, ba\u015flamal\u0131. Ve Allah hesab\u0131yla vermeli ve almal\u0131. Ve izni ve kanunu dairesinde [[davranmal\u0131|hareket etmeli|]], [[huzur bulmal\u0131|s\xfck\xfbnet bulmal\u0131|sakinle\u015fmeli]].\\n\\n[[hata yapsa|Kusur etse|kusur i\u015flese]] [[t\xf6vbe etmeli|isti\u011ffar etmeli|Allah'tan ba\u011f\u0131\u015flanma dilemeli]]. \u201c[[Ey Rabbim|Y\xe2 Rab|]]! Kusurumuzu affet, bizi kendine kul kabul et, emanetini [[teslim almak|kabzetmek|ruhumuzu almak]] zaman\u0131na kadar bizi emanette [[g\xfcvenilir eyle|emin k\u0131l|sad\u0131k k\u0131l]], [[kabul eyle|\xe2min|]]!\u201d demeli ve ona yalvarmal\u0131.\\n***\",\"processedBy\":\"\ud83e\udde0 Gemini 3.0 Pro (Web - Manuel) on 2025.12.17-18:18\",\"lastUpdated\":\"2025-12-25T06:49:19.602Z\",\"oldText\":\"**\xdc\xe7\xfcnc\xfc [[hasaret|zarar|ziyan]]:** B\xfct\xfcn o [[k\u0131ymettar|de\u011ferli|k\u0131ymetli]] [[cihazat-\u0131 insaniyeyi|insani donan\u0131mlar\u0131|insana verilen duygu ve yetenekleri]], hayvanl\u0131ktan \xe7ok a\u015fa\u011f\u0131 bir [[derekeye|a\u015fa\u011f\u0131 dereceye|\xe7ukurun en dibine]] d\xfc\u015f\xfcr\xfcp [[hikmet-i \u0130lahiyeye|Allah'\u0131n hikmetine|Allah'\u0131n her \u015feyi yerli yerinde ve gayeli yaratmas\u0131na]] iftira ve [[zulmettin|haks\u0131zl\u0131k ettin|zul\xfcm yapt\u0131n]].\\n\\n**D\xf6rd\xfcnc\xfc [[hasaret|zarar|ziyan]]:** [[Acz|acizlik|g\xfc\xe7s\xfczl\xfck]] ve [[fakr\u0131n|fakirli\u011fin|ihtiya\xe7 i\xe7inde olu\u015fun]] ile beraber, o pek a\u011f\u0131r hayat y\xfck\xfcn\xfc, zay\u0131f beline y\xfckleyip [[zeval|sona erme|yok olu\u015f, bat\u0131\u015f]] ve [[firak|ayr\u0131l\u0131k]] [[sillesi|tokad\u0131]] alt\u0131nda [[daim|daima|s\xfcrekli]] [[vaveyl\xe2 edeceksin|feryat edeceksin|\xe7\u0131\u011fl\u0131k atacaks\u0131n]].\\n\\n**Be\u015finci [[hasaret|zarar|ziyan]]:** [[Hayat-\u0131 ebediye|sonsuz hayat|ahiret hayat\u0131]] [[esasat\u0131n\u0131|temellerini|esaslar\u0131n\u0131]] ve [[saadet-i uhreviye|ahiret mutlulu\u011fu]] [[levaz\u0131mat\u0131n\u0131|gere\xe7lerini|malzemelerini, ihtiya\xe7lar\u0131n\u0131]] [[tedarik etmek|elde etmek|sa\u011flamak, haz\u0131rlamak]] i\xe7in verilen ak\u0131l, kalp, g\xf6z ve dil gibi g\xfczel [[hediye-i Rahmaniyeyi|Rahman olan Allah'\u0131n hediyesini|Merhametli Allah'\u0131n ba\u011f\u0131\u015f\u0131n\u0131]], cehennem kap\u0131lar\u0131n\u0131 sana a\xe7acak \xe7irkin bir [[surete|bi\xe7ime|\u015fekle, g\xf6r\xfcn\xfcme]] \xe7evirmektir.\\n\\n\u015eimdi satmaya bakaca\u011f\u0131z. Acaba o kadar a\u011f\u0131r bir \u015fey midir ki \xe7oklar\u0131 satmaktan ka\xe7\u0131yorlar. Yok, [[kat\u2019\xe2|kesinlikle]] ve [[asl\xe2|asla|hi\xe7bir zaman]]! Hi\xe7 \xf6yle a\u011f\u0131rl\u0131\u011f\u0131 yoktur. [[Zira|\xe7\xfcnk\xfc]] hel\xe2l dairesi geni\u015ftir, keyfe [[k\xe2fi gelir|yeter|yeterli gelir]]. Harama girmeye hi\xe7 [[l\xfczum|gerek|ihtiya\xe7]] yoktur. [[Feraiz-i \u0130lahiye|Allah'\u0131n farzlar\u0131|Allah'\u0131n emretti\u011fi zorunlu g\xf6revler]] ise hafiftir, azd\u0131r.\\n\\nAllah\u2019a [[abd|kul|k\xf6le]] ve asker olmak, \xf6yle lezzetli bir \u015fereftir ki tarif edilmez.\\n\\nVazife ise yaln\u0131z, bir asker gibi Allah [[nam\u0131na|ad\u0131na]] i\u015flemeli, ba\u015flamal\u0131. Ve Allah hesab\u0131yla vermeli ve almal\u0131. Ve izni ve kanunu dairesinde [[hareket etmeli|davranmal\u0131]], [[s\xfck\xfbnet bulmal\u0131|huzur bulmal\u0131|sakinle\u015fmeli]].\\n\\n[[Kusur etse|hata yapsa|kusur i\u015flese]] [[isti\u011ffar etmeli|t\xf6vbe etmeli|Allah'tan ba\u011f\u0131\u015flanma dilemeli]]. \u201c[[Y\xe2 Rab|Ey Rabbim]]! Kusurumuzu affet, bizi kendine kul kabul et, emanetini [[kabzetmek|teslim almak|ruhumuzu almak]] zaman\u0131na kadar bizi emanette [[emin k\u0131l|g\xfcvenilir eyle|sad\u0131k k\u0131l]], [[\xe2min|kabul eyle]]!\u201d demeli ve ona yalvarmal\u0131.\\n***\"}]")}}]);